Class Admin

java.lang.Object
src.Customer
src.Admin
public class Admin extends Customer
Admin IS-A customer with a bottomless card. This is the default login state for anyone starting the CFG Shop program. This class creates the Admin as a Customer with 1 billion dollars and a card number of one. There can be multiple admins at one time.
